  <title> Configuring <app>Accerciser</app></title>
  <p>
    To configure plugins, hotkeys, and highlighting, do either <key>ctrl</key>+<key>p</key> or <guiseq><gui>Edit</gui>
    <gui>Preferences</gui></guiseq> to open a dialog.
  </p>

